Butler of the Commercial Pacific Cable Company, Midway; purple stamp “Midway May 11 1935” above; signed by Mr. Butler and the flight crew of flight 4-P-3; postmarked May 1, 1935, U.S.S. Beaver at Midway Islands and June 1, [no year], Columbus, Ohio; backstamp: May 24, 1935, Fleet Air Base, Pearl Harbor; text on reverse: “ Cachet by courtesy of West Coast Airmail Society” of San Francisco.b.
